=Description=

“Collaborative Cities is a participatory webdocumentary. In the most vibrant cities, we will meet inspiring people who create and participate in collaborative services and experiences. With you, we will experience what the collaborative economy has to offer from flat sharing, skill sharing, to co-working, and even more.

A project directed by Maxime Leroy and made possible by the OuiShare community.”


